---
title: Easy One-Pot Italian Chicken Orecchiette with Baby Leaves & Parmesan
description: Orecchiette has to be our favourite pasta shape, the little pockets are perfect for scooping up flavour! Stir through herby, juicy chicken thigh and tender veggies for a saucy dish that guarantees a table full of smiling faces.

*We’ve replaced the risoni in this recipe with orecchiette due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
